Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Linamon in the Province of Lanao Del Norte to Tomas Cabili
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 365
An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Linamon in the Province of Lanao Del Norte to Tomas Cabili
Section 1. The name of the Municipality of Linamon in the Province of Lanao del Norte is changed to Tomas Cabili.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 7, 1983
